collapse of the north tower.

00:06:37.140 --> 00:06:42.850 align:middle line:84%
So this was a monumental event,
and why has this not been

00:06:42.850 --> 00:06:44.840 align:middle line:90%
shown on Danish television?

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:49.260 align:middle line:90%
Why did I not know this?

00:06:49.260 --> 00:06:51.640 align:middle line:90%
That was shocking.

00:06:51.640 --> 00:06:55.000 align:middle line:84%
And the next thing
relates to my training

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:58.110 align:middle line:84%
as an actual
scientist, because it

00:06:58.110 --> 00:07:05.890 align:middle line:84%
is my job-- I've been trained
to see my physical environment

00:07:05.890 --> 00:07:08.060 align:middle line:90%
with an analytical mind.

00:07:08.060 --> 00:07:13.090 align:middle line:84%
Whenever I see something,
I involuntarily try

00:07:13.090 --> 00:07:14.760 align:middle line:90%
to figure out how it's working.

00:07:14.760 --> 00:07:17.210 align:middle line:90%
And why does this happen?

00:07:17.210 --> 00:07:18.200 align:middle line:90%
Why does this happen?

00:07:18.200 --> 00:07:24.390 align:middle line:84%
This is the bend of any
natural scientist's nature.

00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:27.380 align:middle line:84%
And most of the time,
I'm doing pretty well.

00:07:27.380 --> 00:07:29.840 align:middle line:90%
