00:09:24.900 --> 00:09:28.870 align:middle line:84%
There were three skyscrapers
collapsing on that day.

00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:30.820 align:middle line:90%
The twin towers.

00:09:30.820 --> 00:09:33.920 align:middle line:84%
The first one was collapsing a
little bit before 10 o'clock.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:35.840 align:middle line:90%
The other one at half past 10.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.910 align:middle line:84%
The twin towers,
the South Tower was

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:39.660 align:middle line:90%
collapsing-- collapsing first.

00:09:39.660 --> 00:09:42.730 align:middle line:84%
The North Tower
collapsing the latest.

00:09:42.730 --> 00:09:45.320 align:middle line:84%
And then this
Building Seven which

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:48.020 align:middle line:90%
collapsed seven hours later.

00:09:48.020 --> 00:09:52.530 align:middle line:84%
And we are told that
these three collapses

00:09:52.530 --> 00:09:55.530 align:middle line:84%
were caused by the impact
of the two airliners.

00:09:55.530 --> 00:09:58.060 align:middle line:90%
That is a lie.

00:09:58.060 --> 00:10:03.300 align:middle line:84%
From a scientific point of view,
no matter how you twist or turn

00:10:03.300 --> 00:10:06.670 align:middle line:84%
the evidence which
is very important,

00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:12.060 align:middle line:84%
there is no physical
connection between the impact

00:10:12.060 --> 00:10:14.700 align:middle line:84%
of the two airliners
and the collapse

00:10:14.700 --> 00:10:16.490 align:middle line:90%
of the three skyscrapers.

00:10:16.490 --> 00:10:19.100 align:middle line:90%
It's simply not true.

00:10:19.100 --> 00:10:21.120 align:middle line:90%
So we have been told a lie.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:28.660 align:middle line:84%
And when I'm saying this, I'm
not referring to weaknesses.

00:10:28.660 --> 00:10:31.260 align:middle line:90%
I'm not referring to rumors.

00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:34.330 align:middle line:84%
I'm not referring
to assumptions.

00:10:34.330 --> 00:10:40.120 align:middle line:84%
I'm referring to the basic
laws of physics and chemistry.

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:44.970 align:middle line:84%
The official version,
namely that these three

00:10:44.970 --> 00:10:49.860 align:middle line:84%
skyscrapers came down due to
fires, that is very short.

00:10:49.860 --> 00:10:52.060 align:middle line:84%
The official version that
the three skyscrapers

00:10:52.060 --> 00:10:54.440 align:middle line:90%
came down due two fires.

00:10:54.440 --> 00:10:59.590 align:middle line:84%
It is-- this explanation
is-- is violating

00:10:59.590 --> 00:11:01.100 align:middle line:90%
basic principles of science.

00:11:01.100 --> 00:11:04.980 align:middle line:84%
And I'm talking
about-- I have to bring

00:11:04.980 --> 00:11:08.640 align:middle line:84%
in Sir Isaac Newton,
the name of who

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:10.850 align:middle line:90%
should be known to everybody.

00:11:10.850 --> 00:11:15.140 align:middle line:84%
His tomb is in Westminster
Abbey in London

00:11:15.140 --> 00:11:16.890 align:middle line:90%
for very good reasons.

00:11:16.890 --> 00:11:22.210 align:middle line:84%
Because he was one of the first
giants of natural science.

00:11:22.210 --> 00:11:26.780 align:middle line:84%
And he wrote a book
which came out in 1687.

00:11:26.780 --> 00:11:34.430 align:middle line:84%
It's called "Principia", and
it describes how bodies move

00:11:34.430 --> 00:11:37.020 align:middle line:90%
in the physical world here.

00:11:37.020 --> 00:11:39.610 align:middle line:90%
Fundamental laws.

00:11:39.610 --> 00:11:44.660 align:middle line:84%
And most people who have taken
physics courses in high school

00:11:44.660 --> 00:11:48.750 align:middle line:84%
have had heard about
Newton's Three Laws.

00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:56.620 align:middle line:84%
And for 300-- I have to make a
rough calculation-- 325 years,

00:11:56.620 --> 00:12:00.300 align:middle line:84%
these laws have
proven indispensable.

00:12:00.300 --> 00:12:02.350 align:middle line:90%
That you cannot break.

00:12:02.350 --> 00:12:05.290 align:middle line:84%
There's no exception
from Newton's Laws.

00:12:05.290 --> 00:12:10.040 align:middle line:84%
And the official explanation
is violating at least two

00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:11.200 align:middle line:90%
of these laws.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:17.340 align:middle line:84%
That is, I'm referring
to physical principles

00:12:17.340 --> 00:12:22.380 align:middle line:84%
which are so fundamental that
there is no way around them.

00:12:22.380 --> 00:12:27.930 align:middle line:84%
So the official explanation for
the collapses of World Trade

00:12:27.930 --> 00:12:32.630 align:middle line:90%
Center is a scientific fraud.

00:12:32.630 --> 00:12:35.560 align:middle line:90%
It's-- it's a lie.

