00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:50.060 align:middle line:84%
NIELS HARRIT: Well, the easiest
thing here to understand

00:12:50.060 --> 00:12:52.670 align:middle line:84%
is the collapse of Building
Seven, the last one,

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:56.170 align:middle line:84%
because that is the
most clean cut example.

00:12:56.170 --> 00:13:01.280 align:middle line:84%
And that's why-- the government,
it took them 7 years, actually,

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:05.370 align:middle line:84%
to come with the technical
account for that collapse.

00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:08.720 align:middle line:84%
They postponed this
report for seven years

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:11.340 align:middle line:84%
until they couldn't
hold back anymore.

00:13:11.340 --> 00:13:16.520 align:middle line:84%
Because what you saw is
this 47-story skyscraper

00:13:16.520 --> 00:13:19.650 align:middle line:84%
coming down, as I told you,
completely symmetrical.

00:13:19.650 --> 00:13:24.300 align:middle line:84%
And it's very easy to
make-- to measure how

00:13:24.300 --> 00:13:27.460 align:middle line:90%
fast this collapse is going.

00:13:27.460 --> 00:13:33.560 align:middle line:84%
And the 47th story, when it--
it-- when it starts to move,

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:37.490 align:middle line:84%
it goes into what
we call free fall.

00:13:37.490 --> 00:13:42.380 align:middle line:84%
It means that it moves, it
accelerates to the ground,

00:13:42.380 --> 00:13:47.970 align:middle line:84%
with exactly the same speed
as an object falling freely.

00:13:47.970 --> 00:13:51.751 align:middle line:84%
I mean, let's-- try with myself.
We'll see.

00:13:51.751 --> 00:13:54.210 align:middle line:84%
Now, watch this.
OK, I release it.

00:13:54.210 --> 00:13:56.160 align:middle line:90%
OK, it goes like that.

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:57.550 align:middle line:90%
There is no resistance.

00:13:57.550 --> 00:13:59.640 align:middle line:84%
It is falling
absolutely free fall,

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.610 align:middle line:84%
and it's actually
accelerating when

00:14:01.610 --> 00:14:03.460 align:middle line:90%
it falls towards the ground.

00:14:03.460 --> 00:14:07.980 align:middle line:84%
This is what happened
to the 47th floor

00:14:07.980 --> 00:14:10.670 align:middle line:90%
of World Trade Center 7.

00:14:10.670 --> 00:14:14.460 align:middle line:84%
So the moment it
starts to move, there

00:14:14.460 --> 00:14:20.690 align:middle line:84%
is absolutely no supporting
structure left in the building.

00:14:20.690 --> 00:14:25.630 align:middle line:84%
Every-- and this building
was designed-- there were

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:28.700 align:middle line:90%
24 core columns, very sturdy.

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:30.980 align:middle line:84%
They were carrying
between 60% and 70%

00:14:30.980 --> 00:14:32.830 align:middle line:90%
of the weight of the building.

00:14:32.830 --> 00:14:37.050 align:middle line:84%
And then there were 57
perimeter columns all the way

00:14:37.050 --> 00:14:39.550 align:middle line:90%
in the-- in the perimeter.

00:14:39.550 --> 00:14:41.950 align:middle line:84%
Now, when the building
started to move,

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:46.530 align:middle line:84%
all these columns
had to be removed.

00:14:46.530 --> 00:14:50.080 align:middle line:84%
There were nothing
supporting the 47th story.

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:53.270 align:middle line:84%
If some idiot has been
standing on the 47th floor,

00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:56.860 align:middle line:84%
and released, say a
stone, out of the window,

00:14:56.860 --> 00:15:00.665 align:middle line:84%
the stone would have moved
at exactly the same speed

00:15:00.665 --> 00:15:03.780 align:middle line:90%
as the 47th story.

00:15:03.780 --> 00:15:08.530 align:middle line:84%
This can only be accomplished
by means of explosives.

00:15:08.530 --> 00:15:14.220 align:middle line:84%
This is what you call a
controlled demolition.

00:15:14.220 --> 00:15:19.720 align:middle line:84%
That is when you are taking
down skyscrapers on purpose.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:24.320 align:middle line:84%
You bring in explosives, you put
the explosives in the building.

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:27.230 align:middle line:84%
And this has been done-- it
has to be done very accurately.

00:15:27.230 --> 00:15:29.630 align:middle line:90%
This is expert work.

00:15:29.630 --> 00:15:32.290 align:middle line:84%
And the collapse of World
Trade Center, the controlled

00:15:32.290 --> 00:15:34.330 align:middle line:84%
demolitions of
World Trade Center

00:15:34.330 --> 00:15:39.240 align:middle line:90%
are masterpieces in engineering.

00:15:39.240 --> 00:15:42.910 align:middle line:84%
They're-- it's so
brilliantly performed.

00:15:42.910 --> 00:15:48.280 align:middle line:84%
No building--
Building 7, 30% higher

00:15:48.280 --> 00:15:53.620 align:middle line:84%
than any building which, at
that time, had been demolished.

00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:59.540 align:middle line:84%
And the twin towers, of
course, three times higher

00:15:59.540 --> 00:16:00.880 align:middle line:90%
than any building at that time.

00:16:00.880 --> 00:16:01.830 align:middle line:90%
It would be different.

00:16:01.830 --> 00:16:05.970 align:middle line:84%
But the story of the
mechanism for the demolition

00:16:05.970 --> 00:16:08.980 align:middle line:84%
of the twin towers is different
from that of Building 7

00:16:08.980 --> 00:16:14.550 align:middle line:84%
which everybody can see just
from watching the videos.

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:16.260 align:middle line:84%
But nobody has seen
Building Seven,

00:16:16.260 --> 00:16:17.560 align:middle line:90%
as I started to tell you.

00:16:17.560 --> 00:16:19.680 align:middle line:84%
It's not shown on
mainstream television.

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:23.180 align:middle line:84%
So most people have not
seen Building Seven.

00:16:23.180 --> 00:16:26.660 align:middle line:84%
And already, at that
point, I mean you

00:16:26.660 --> 00:16:28.660 align:middle line:84%
and many other
people may have had

00:16:28.660 --> 00:16:30.600 align:middle line:84%
problems with the
physics classes

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:32.280 align:middle line:90%
and the chemistry classes.

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:35.970 align:middle line:84%
And the teacher was not
very good eventually

00:16:35.970 --> 00:16:38.100 align:middle line:84%
and you didn't understand
a thing and all

00:16:38.100 --> 00:16:39.900 align:middle line:90%
this mathematics stuff, OK.

00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:42.630 align:middle line:90%
But we can all count to three.

00:16:42.630 --> 00:16:46.540 align:middle line:84%
So already from the fact that
there were two airliners,

00:16:46.540 --> 00:16:50.170 align:middle line:84%
but there were three skyscrapers
collapsing on that day.

00:16:50.170 --> 00:16:53.310 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we can count
to three, can we?

00:16:53.310 --> 00:16:56.300 align:middle line:84%
Already from this fact,
you should realize

00:16:56.300 --> 00:16:59.080 align:middle line:90%
that there is something wrong.

00:16:59.080 --> 00:17:03.635 align:middle line:84%
And the way it is
collapsing is unambiguously

00:17:03.635 --> 00:17:05.609 align:middle line:90%
a controlled demolition.

00:17:05.609 --> 00:17:09.750 align:middle line:84%
And this can only be done
by means of explosives

00:17:09.750 --> 00:17:13.040 align:middle line:84%
and something else which
is called incendiaries.

00:17:13.040 --> 00:17:18.530 align:middle line:84%
We know about World Trade Center
that it is-- that actually

00:17:18.530 --> 00:17:24.660 align:middle line:84%
the steel columns were cut in--
by other means than explosives,

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:26.730 align:middle line:90%
but explosives were used.

00:17:26.730 --> 00:17:32.200 align:middle line:84%
It is-- it is necessary for
accomplishing this completely

00:17:32.200 --> 00:17:38.210 align:middle line:84%
symmetrical and this free
fall feature of its collapse

00:17:38.210 --> 00:17:39.310 align:middle line:90%
to the ground.

00:17:39.310 --> 00:17:44.790 align:middle line:84%
This, I repeat, this
requires that at that moment,

00:17:44.790 --> 00:17:48.480 align:middle line:84%
all supporting structure
of the building is gone.

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:51.620 align:middle line:84%
And since it's falling
completely symmetrically,

00:17:51.620 --> 00:17:54.510 align:middle line:84%
it means that it's
gone at the same time.

00:17:54.510 --> 00:17:56.120 align:middle line:90%
There's no way around this.

00:17:56.120 --> 00:18:02.100 align:middle line:84%
So that's why maybe somebody
don't show Building 7.

00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:07.060 align:middle line:84%
It's really the Achilles's
heel or, what you would say?

00:18:07.060 --> 00:18:10.760 align:middle line:90%
The smoking gun.

00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:13.800 align:middle line:84%
LILOU MACE: And that building,
it was--was it 5 o'clock?

00:18:13.800 --> 00:18:14.980 align:middle line:90%
Or much later?

