00:24:54.970 --> 00:24:57.460 align:middle line:90%
of course, are explosives.

00:24:57.460 --> 00:25:02.740 align:middle line:84%
But there are other
means to cut steel beams,

00:25:02.740 --> 00:25:06.040 align:middle line:84%
and that is by means
of incendiaries.

00:25:06.040 --> 00:25:11.890 align:middle line:84%
And an incendiary is-- is--
is an energetic material which

00:25:11.890 --> 00:25:15.460 align:middle line:84%
works by means of heat
while an explosive

00:25:15.460 --> 00:25:16.930 align:middle line:90%
works by means of pressure.

