We had a new law, actually,
for-- for governance of

00:40:46.050 --> 00:40:49.150 align:middle line:90%
the Danish universities 2003.

00:40:49.150 --> 00:40:50.440 align:middle line:90%
Up to that point.

00:40:50.440 --> 00:40:56.500 align:middle line:84%
The University of
Copenhagen is from 1488.

