ruled by the government.

00:41:25.350 --> 00:41:28.850 align:middle line:84%
And this is-- has happening all
over in the Western societies.

00:41:28.850 --> 00:41:30.120 align:middle line:90%
That's one mechanism.

00:41:30.120 --> 00:41:32.950 align:middle line:84%
The other mechanism
lies in the funding,

00:41:32.950 --> 00:41:34.460 align:middle line:90%
where the money comes from.

00:41:34.460 --> 00:41:40.220 align:middle line:84%
So what I see now is all my
