00:43:28.810 --> 00:43:30.790 align:middle line:84%
And they're called
first responders.

00:43:30.790 --> 00:43:33.830 align:middle line:84%
And of course, there were all
the firemen, all the policemen,

00:43:33.830 --> 00:43:36.260 align:middle line:90%
all the workers on the site.

00:43:36.260 --> 00:43:38.860 align:middle line:84%
Many, many thousands
of these people

00:43:38.860 --> 00:43:42.960 align:middle line:84%
have come-- become ill because
